{"tid":1568543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪都話要人，要人前你諗清楚結果先好冇","createTime":"2019-09-14T10:09:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T12:51:00.000Z","uid":20209,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"67a9dc1319da07748818c2bb24c53e0e24e498ba","tid":1568543,"uid":20209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:09:29.000Z","msg":"今日藍絲遊行，你要人做乜<br />\n得嗰500人唱狗歌，有乜好踩場<br />\n新聞就算報都係話幾丁人咋嘛<br />\n200萬人唔夠？170萬人唔夠？<br />\n你出到去又唔係打柒班藍絲hit n run<br />\n竟然去唱歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要唔夠人比藍絲打 完全係唔撚化算 <br />\n你話斬咗幾個人咁比人拉 咁冇嘢講啦 <br />\n啱先有勇武手足想打 仲要比人拉住 佢幾撚失望呀<br />\n<br />\n警犬一早準備好晒捉依啲小貓幾隻咖<br />\n乜嘢打人唔撚拉只拉後生 依啲你第一日知咩<br />\n結果你哋班唱歌既比人打就比人拉 <br />\n啱啱最新新聞打落單藍絲嘔血既就啱啦 <br />\n<br />\n要人前要諗你出嚟做乜嘢 有冇伏 有冇鬼 <br />\n成日話要人話人當手足condom<br />\n根本亂叫人出嚟既先係當手足condom<br />\n<br />\n黑心講 手足比人打比人亂拉 甚至死咗呀<br />\n我哋又多粒子彈用<br />\n但真心唔想大家為依啲嘢比人拉 子彈我哋有<br />\n大家要沉住氣呀 政府就係沉得住氣得閒譴責下捉幾個拮你幾刀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n温多啲毛語錄啦"},{"pid":"040b6e640e4d272c28dc5a53c883cf7bc1ac02c2","tid":1568543,"uid":20209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:10:51.000Z","msg":"Right time<br />\nRight things<br />\nRight places ar<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b3c208469ec8a6ffe2215dfc2c8445661d21ad1","tid":1568543,"uid":23752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:17:19.000Z","msg":"認同 唔係話唔去打唔去救 但我覺得出得去就要有十足把握同決心 出到去又唔係打狗只係唱歌同嗌放人只會增加手足犧牲機會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點做都好 大家記住<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不指責 不分化 不割蓆 不篤</span></span>灰"},{"pid":"7b0ebf33ea2d37d49ebd6ac6ea1ef78b44ea9200","tid":1568543,"uid":20209,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:17:19.000Z","msg":"何謂送頭<br />\n<br />\n有勇武心冇覺悟既就係送頭<br />\n冇勇武心冇覺悟既直頭係害手足"},{"pid":"dca9600a17c2a371770860f8e09164de1d85b446","tid":1568543,"uid":258592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:18:08.000Z","msg":"要諗成效 <br />\n唔好手足前手足後道德綁架"},{"pid":"088477fba7a4bdeb4256812bfb1a29ac87635af4","tid":1568543,"uid":20209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dca9600a17c2a371770860f8e09164de1d85b446","tid":1568543,"uid":258592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:18:08.000Z","msg":"要諗成效 <br />\n唔好手足前手足後道德綁架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:22:05.000Z","msg":"冇錯"},{"pid":"45ca2365a2d759663ed64bf8541cbf07644fcb6a","tid":1568543,"uid":257422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:22:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仆你個臭街！<br />\n今日死差佬同藍絲又周圍打人！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n聽日九月十五日<br />\n<br />\n2pm<br />\n 銅鑼灣東角道 /<br />\n維園 / 英領<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> 全人類同我出黎！<br />\n唔係我屌埋你老母呀！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/newsfeed/000/915/652/b49.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kym-cdn.com%2Fphotos%2Fimages%2Fnewsfeed%2F000%2F915%2F652%2Fb49.gif&h=c007be28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</span></div></span>"},{"pid":"ddc259cf776264f369c49525fadf2c6fcce54364","tid":1568543,"uid":20209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:22:37.000Z","msg":"今日搞一搞 聽日又少幾個。。。"},{"pid":"519e4f528e4278015dc80f066f04f10887d8236d","tid":1568543,"uid":107297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:24:26.000Z","msg":"連登根本有鬼瘋狂要人送頭"},{"pid":"da0375571fe8f56bd0e166769ab678ea06838f47","tid":1568543,"uid":20209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"519e4f528e4278015dc80f066